title: Man from Snowy River and other Verses, The
creator: Paterson, Andrew Barton
description: LibriVox recording of The Man from Snowy River and other Verses, by Andrew Barton 'Banjo" Paterson A collection of poems by Australian poet Andrew Barton 'Banjo' Paterson, picturesque glimpses into life in the Bush. From the preface: "A number of these verses are now published for the first time, most of the others were written for and appeared in 'The Bulletin' (Sydney, N.S.W.), and are therefore already widely known to readers in Australasia." (Summary by Tricia G.) For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
